videos.headline: Houston strikes first with 33-yd TD
videos.description: Clayton Tune hits Terry Mark on a 33-yard touchdown to put the Cougars on the board against the Memphis Tigers.

videos.headline: Houston sacked on 4th down
videos.description: Bryce Huff sacks Cougars QB Clayton Tune for a five-yard loss on 4th and 6.

videos.headline: Memphis punches in 7-yd TD
videos.description: Patrick Taylor Jr. plows through the Houston defense to score for the Tigers in the second quarter.

videos.headline: Oliver with costly penalty in red zone
videos.description: Ed Oliver gets pulled from the drive after picking up another costly red zone penalty for Houston.

videos.headline: White finds Magnifico for 9-yd TD
videos.description: Brady White hits Joey Magnifico for a touchdown, extending Memphis' lead over Houston 17-7.

videos.headline: Oliver leads Houston's D to sack
videos.description: Ed Oliver and the Cougars' defense collapse the pocket and bring down Tigers QB Brady White.

videos.headline: Houston QB escapes Memphis' D for TD
videos.description: True freshman QB Clayton Tune shakes off two Tigers defenders to find Keith Corbin on a 3-yard TD strike.

videos.headline: Houston scores on pick-6
videos.description: Gleson Sprewell intercepts Brady White's pass and returns it 63 yards for another Houston score.

videos.headline: Memphis picked off in red zone on trick play
videos.description: Gleson Sprewell doesn't fall for Memphis TE Joey Magnifico "falling" at the goal line and patiently intercepts Brady White's pass.

videos.headline: Memphis takes lead without Oliver on field
videos.description: The Tigers take advantage of Ed Oliver being on the sidelines as Sam Craft breaks loose for a 28-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Oliver benched for 2nd half
videos.description: Ed Oliver will not return to the field for the second half against Memphis.

videos.headline: Memphis takes lead on the ground
videos.description: Tony Pollard runs in a 6-yard touchdown to take the lead vs. Houston 30-24.

videos.headline: Corbin spins in for game-tying TD
videos.description: Clayton Tune hits Keith Corbin on a 45-yard touchdown to tie it with Memphis at 31.

videos.headline: Memphis scores on 3rd straight drive while Oliver sidelined
videos.description: The Tigers take full advantage of Ed Oliver being absent from the defense with another rushing touchdown.

videos.headline: Henderson streaks downfield for 60-yd score
videos.description: Darrell Henderson runs for a 60-yard touchdown against the Houston in the fourth quarter.

videos.headline: Memphis easily scores to extend lead
videos.description: Darrell Henderson scores his second TD of the fourth quarter to give Memphis a 52-31 lead over Houston.

videos.headline: Houston picked off in end zone
videos.description: T.J. Carter intercepts Clayton Tune's end-zone pass late in the fourth quarter.
